===============
 Documentation
===============

Documentation is currently maintained as Sphinx sources in the docs directory
of this project.

Current online documentation is here:

  http://thatclevershark.org

To build the documentation, you need Sphinx installed:

  easy_install sphinx

If you don't have easy_install installed, see:

  http://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools.

If you have a standard package manager such as apt-get or yum, search for
python-setuptools or similar.
